gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: This GIS layer shows the locations of ethanol production facilities in the state of Indiana. Attributes include the name and address of the facility, and information regarding ethanol production capacity.

gmd:purpose.gco:CharacterString: This GIS layer was developed to show the locations of ethanol production facilities in Indiana.

gmd:supplementalInformation.gco:CharacterString: Information regarding ethanol production facilities was obtained from the following sources -- (1) Fact Sheet - Biofuel Plants in Indiana at http://www.in.gov/isda/biofuels/factsheet.pdf (2) Indiana Ethanol Plants -- Purdue University at http://cobweb.ecn.purdue.edu/~lorre/16/Biofuel%20Factsheets/pdms

gmd:measureDescription.gco:CharacterString: All ethanol-production sites listed in the sources cited above are represented in this dataset.

Locations were obtained from two sources (1) Fact Sheet - Biofuel Plants in Indiana at http://www.in.gov/isda/biofuels/factsheet.pdf (2) Indiana Ethanol Plants -- Purdue University at http://cobweb.ecn.purdue.edu/~lorre/16/Biofuel%20Factsheets/pdms Addresses were entered into the Web site named "Mapquest" at http://www.mapquest.com/. Using ESRI ArcMap, a new shapefile named "ETHANOL_PRODUCTION_041811.SHP" was created, and points were added by visual comparison with sites located using Mapquest. Attributes were populated with values obtained from Items 1 and 2, above.
Mapquest (http://www.mapquest.com/) was used to locate the ethanol production facilities. Using ESRI ArcMap, points were added by visual comparison with Mapquest.

gmd:description.gco:CharacterString: Locations were obtained from two sources (1) Fact Sheet - Biofuel Plants in Indiana at http://www.in.gov/isda/biofuels/factsheet.pdf (2) Indiana Ethanol Plants -- Purdue University at http://cobweb.ecn.purdue.edu/~lorre/16/Biofuel%20Factsheets/pdms Addresses were entered into the Web site named "Mapquest" at http://www.mapquest.com/. Using ESRI ArcMap, a new shapefile named "ETHANOL_PRODUCTION_041811.SHP" was created, and points were added by visual comparison with sites located using Mapquest. Attributes were populated with values obtained from Items (1) and (2), above. The shapefile was renamed as "ETHANOL_PRODUCTION_FACILITIES_IN.SHP."
